name: OpioidOralTabletsAndPatchesOnly
title: Opioid (Oral Tablets and Patches only)
description: The intent of this data element is to identify prescriptions for opioid medications.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The intent of this data element is to identify prescriptions for opioid medications.),(Data Element Scope: Opioid in the form of oral tablets and patches.),(Inclusion Criteria: Opioid in the form of oral tablets and patches.),(Exclusion Criteria: Buprenorphine, cough and cold products as well as opioid in the form of oral solution, or injection are excluded from the value set.)
